<h2>Weekly Audit Report</h2>

<p><strong>Report Period:</strong> Week of <%= @from_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d') %></p>
<p><strong>Coverage:</strong> <%= @from_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d') %> through <%= @to_date.localtime.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M %Z') %></p>

<p><strong>Active Tickets:</strong> <%= @ticket_count %></p>

<% if @ticket_count > 0 %>
<p>This report shows all tickets that were created or updated during the current week. This data is used for access list consistency checks.</p>

<p>The complete report data has been attached as a CSV file for your review.</p>

<h3>Summary</h3>
<p>
  Total active tickets: <%= @ticket_count %><br>
  Report generated: <%= Time.now.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z') %>
</p>
<% else %>
<p>No tickets were created or updated during this week.</p>
<% end %>

<hr>
<p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
  This is an automated report from the NY Senate Audit Utils system.
</p>
